#: ../../I/ISO-standard-cup-of-tea.rst:5
msgid "ISO standard cup of tea"
msgstr "ISO standard cup of tea"

#: ../../I/ISO-standard-cup-of-tea.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../I/ISO-standard-cup-of-tea.rst:9
msgid ""
"[South Africa] A cup of tea with milk and one teaspoon of sugar, where the "
"milk is poured into the cup before the tea. Variations are ISO 0, with no "
"sugar; ISO 2, with two spoons of sugar; and so on."
msgstr ""
"[南アフリカ] ミルクと小さじ1杯の砂糖を入れた紅茶で、ミルクを紅茶より先にカップに注いだもの。砂糖なしのISO 0、砂糖を2杯入れたISO "
"2、というように変種がある。"

#: ../../I/ISO-standard-cup-of-tea.rst:12
msgid ""
"This may derive from the \"NATO standard\" cup of coffee and tea (milk and "
"two sugars), military slang going back to the late 1950s and parodying "
"NATO's relentless bureaucratic drive to standardize parts across European "
"and U.S. militaries."
msgstr ""
"これはおそらく「NATO標準」のコーヒーと紅茶(ミルクと砂糖2杯)に由来する。これは1950年代後半にさかのぼる軍隊スラングで、ヨーロッパと米国の軍隊で部品を標準化しようとするNATOの執拗な官僚主義的衝動をパロディ化したものである。"

#: ../../I/ISO-standard-cup-of-tea.rst:14
msgid ""
"Like many ISO standards, this one has a faintly alien ring in North America,"
" where hackers generally shun the decadent British practice of adulterating "
"perfectly good tea with dairy products and prefer instead to add a wedge of "
"lemon, if anything. If one were feeling extremely silly, one might "
"hypothesize an analogous ANSI standard cup of tea and wind up with a "
"political situation distressingly similar to several that arise in much more"
" serious technical contexts. (Milk and lemon don't mix very well.)"
msgstr ""
"多くのISO標準と同様に、これは北米ではかすかに異質な響きを持つ。そこではハッカーは一般に、完璧に良質の紅茶を乳製品で混ぜ物にするという退廃的なイギリスの習慣を避け、代わりに(何か入れるとしても)レモンのくし切りを加えるほうを好む。もし極めてばかげた気分なら、それに類似のANSI標準の紅茶を仮定してみて、はるかに深刻な技術的文脈で生じるいくつかの状況と痛々しいほど似た政治的状況に行き着くかもしれない。(ミルクとレモンはあまりよく混ざらない。)"

#: ../../I/ISO-standard-cup-of-tea.rst:18
msgid ""
"[2000 update: There is now, in fact, an ISO standard 3103: ‘Method for "
"preparation of a liquor of tea for use in sensory tests.’, alleged to be "
"equivalent to British Standard BS6008: *How to make a standard cup of tea.* "
"—ESR]"
msgstr ""
"[2000年の更新:実は今や、ISO標準3103『感覚試験に用いる紅茶液の調製法』というものが実在し、イギリス規格BS6008『標準的な紅茶の淹れ方』に相当するとされている。—ESR]"
